This is the UI for the federated bird app.

it's scaffolded from yeoman (http://yeoman.io/) angular template.

it should install using (it needs npm, bower & grunt)
$ npm install
$ bower install

Dev server can be launched using:
$ grunt server

Also
$ grunt build
generate an app that can be hosted on any http server

Currently it requires the federated bird API to answer on "localhost:5000" (This can be configured at the end of index.html)
